name: feature-tree
description: "Manage feature trees with WBS-linked task states. Use when
  organizing work into hierarchical feature trees, tracking feature status
  roll-up (backlog → validated → executing → done), or linking features to task
  IDs. Triggers: show features, feature tree, link WBS to feature, check feature
  status, digest feature."
version: 1.0.0
emoji: 🛠️
